{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, the authors highlighted that the proposed model exhibited robustness against noise.The combination of two types of ANNs has demonstrated effectiveness in the work of Safarzadeh and Jafarzadeh [63].",
    "The authors utilized a CNN-BLSTM-CTC hybrid model for AHCR, AHDR, and AHWR.",
    "This same combination was used by [29] for word segmentation (refer to Sect. 3.1.)",
    "but with differences in the architecture.",
    "The model begins with ten stacked convolutional layers generating 512 feature vectors of size 16 (Table 4)."
  ]
}